{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":325,"text":"Good morning."},{"time":1509,"text":"My name is David Rose."},{"time":2793,"text":"I am a serial entrepreneur\nturned serial investor."},{"time":6373,"text":"And by the use of pitching\nPowerPoints to VCs,"},{"time":9993,"text":"I have personally raised\ntens of millions of dollars"},{"time":12493,"text":"from VCs through PowerPoint pitches."},{"time":15387,"text":"And turning to the other side\nof the equation,"},{"time":17589,"text":"I've personally supervised the investment\nof tens of millions of dollars"},{"time":21029,"text":"into companies who have pitched me\nwith PowerPoint presentations."},{"time":24120,"text":"So I think it's safe to say"},{"time":25469,"text":"I know a little bit\nabout the process of pitching."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28145,"text":"So, the very first question\nyou've got to figure out is:"},{"time":30801,"text":"What is the single most important\nthing that a VC is looking for"},{"time":34483,"text":"when you come to them\npitching your new business idea?"},{"time":37625,"text":"There are obviously all kinds of things --"},{"time":39654,"text":"business models and financials\nand markets and this and that."},{"time":42560,"text":"Overall, of all the things\nthat you have to do,"},{"time":44790,"text":"what is the single most important thing"},{"time":46721,"text":"the VC is going to be investing in?"},{"time":49743,"text":"Somebody? What?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":51000,"text":"Audience: People!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":52502,"text":"David Rose: People! You!\nThat's it -- you are the person."},{"time":55905,"text":"Therefore, the entire purpose\nof a VC pitch is to convince them"},{"time":59805,"text":"that you are the entrepreneur in whom\nthey are going to invest their money"},{"time":63423,"text":"and make a lot of money in return."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65337,"text":"Now, how do you do this?"},{"time":66528,"text":"You can't just walk up and say,"},{"time":68052,"text":"\"Hi, I'm a really good guy, good girl,\nand you should invest in me.\" Right?"},{"time":72020,"text":"So in the course of your VC pitch --\nyou have a very few minutes;"},{"time":75618,"text":"most VC pitches, angel pitches,\nare about 15 minutes,"},{"time":78755,"text":"most should be less than half an hour --"},{"time":81199,"text":"people's attention span,\nafter 18 minutes, begins to drop off."},{"time":84141,"text":"Tests have shown."},{"time":85316,"text":"So in that 18 or 10 or five minutes,"},{"time":87535,"text":"you have to convey a whole bunch\nof different characteristics,"},{"time":90495,"text":"about 10 different characteristics,"},{"time":92581,"text":"while you're standing up there."},{"time":94098,"text":"What's the single most important thing\nyou've got to convey? What?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":97736,"text":"Audience: Integrity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":98954,"text":"DR: Boy, oh boy, oh boy!"},{"time":100177,"text":"That's a straight line, look at that!"},{"time":101987,"text":"And I didn't even prompt him."},{"time":103408,"text":"Right, integrity. The key thing."},{"time":105360,"text":"I would much rather invest in,\ntake a chance on,"},{"time":108392,"text":"somebody who I know is straight\nthan where there's any possible question"},{"time":112043,"text":"of who are they looking out for,\nand what's going on."},{"time":114565,"text":"So the most important thing is integrity."},{"time":116573,"text":"What's the second most important thing?"},{"time":118691,"text":"Let's see if you can get this one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120341,"text":"Audience: Self-confidence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121671,"text":"DR: Close enough. Passion."},{"time":123718,"text":"Right? Entrepreneurs, by definition,\nare people who are leaving something else,"},{"time":127555,"text":"starting a new world, creating and putting\ntheir lifeblood into this thing."},{"time":131261,"text":"You've got to convey passion."},{"time":132670,"text":"If you're not passionate,"},{"time":133997,"text":"why should anyone else be,\nor put money into your company"},{"time":137173,"text":"if you're not passionate about it?"},{"time":138888,"text":"Integrity, passion:\nthe most important things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":141220,"text":"Then there's a whole panoply\nof other things you've got to wrap up"},{"time":144425,"text":"in this package you're presenting to a VC."},{"time":146639,"text":"Experience: you've got to be able to say,"},{"time":148717,"text":"\"Hey, you know, I've done this before.\""},{"time":150899,"text":"\"Done this before\" is starting\nan enterprise, creating value,"},{"time":153959,"text":"and taking something\nfrom beginning to end."},{"time":155992,"text":"That's why VCs love to fund\nserial entrepreneurs --"},{"time":158531,"text":"even if you didn't do it right\nthe first time,"},{"time":160707,"text":"you've learned the lessons, which puts\nyou in good stead the next time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164070,"text":"Along with the experience of starting\nan enterprise or running something --"},{"time":167647,"text":"doesn't have to be a business,"},{"time":169117,"text":"it can be an organization\nin a school, a not-for-profit."},{"time":171847,"text":"But experience\nin creating an organization."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173925,"text":"Next: knowledge."},{"time":175100,"text":"If you tell me"},{"time":176275,"text":"you're going to be the developer\nof the map of the human genome,"},{"time":179330,"text":"you better know what a human genome is;\nI want you to have expertise."},{"time":182744,"text":"I don't want somebody who says,"},{"time":184253,"text":"\"I've got a great idea\nin a business I know nothing about."},{"time":187000,"text":"I don't know who the players are,\nwhat the market is like.\""},{"time":189803,"text":"You've got to know your market, your area."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191843,"text":"And you have to have\nthe skills that it takes"},{"time":193970,"text":"to get a company going."},{"time":195144,"text":"Those skills include\neverything from technical skills"},{"time":198241,"text":"if it's a technology business,"},{"time":199987,"text":"to marketing and sales\nand management and so on."},{"time":202785,"text":"But, you know, not everybody\nhas all these skills."},{"time":205491,"text":"Very few people have the full set\nof skills it takes to run a company."}]},{"cues":[{"time":209210,"text":"What else do you require?\nWell, leadership."},{"time":211261,"text":"You've got to be able to convince us\nthat you either have developed a team"},{"time":214791,"text":"that has all those factors\nin it, or else you can."},{"time":217639,"text":"And you have the charisma\nand the management style"},{"time":220094,"text":"and the ability to get people\nto follow your lead,"},{"time":222897,"text":"to inspire them, to motivate them\nto be part of your team."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226209,"text":"Having done all that,"},{"time":227781,"text":"what else do I want to know as a VC?"},{"time":229526,"text":"I want to know that you have commitment."},{"time":231645,"text":"That you are going to be here to the end."},{"time":233630,"text":"I want you to say --\nor I want you to convey --"},{"time":236276,"text":"that you are going to die if you\nhave to, with your very last breath,"},{"time":239924,"text":"your fingernails scratching\nas they draw you out."},{"time":242274,"text":"You'll keep my money alive\nand make more from it."},{"time":244774,"text":"I don't want someone who'll\ncut and run at the first opportunity."},{"time":247856,"text":"Bad things happen."},{"time":249031,"text":"There's never been a venture-funded\ncompany where bad things didn't happen."},{"time":252596,"text":"So know that you're committed\nto the very end."}]},{"cues":[{"time":254765,"text":"You've got to have vision\nto see where this is going."},{"time":257385,"text":"I don't want another \"me too\" product."},{"time":259222,"text":"I want somebody who can\nchange the world out there."},{"time":261672,"text":"But on top of that, I need realism,"},{"time":263368,"text":"Because while changing the world\nis great, it doesn't always happen."},{"time":267549,"text":"And before you get to change the world,"},{"time":269502,"text":"bad things are going to take place;"},{"time":271197,"text":"you have to deal with that."},{"time":272549,"text":"And you have to have rational projections."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274578,"text":"Finally, you're asking for my money --"},{"time":276521,"text":"not just because it's my money,\nbut because it's me."},{"time":278979,"text":"You need to be coachable."},{"time":280199,"text":"I need to know\nyou have the ability to listen."},{"time":282374,"text":"We've had a lot of experience."},{"time":283838,"text":"People who are VCs or angels\ninvesting in you have had experience,"},{"time":287141,"text":"and they'd like to know that you\nwant to hear that experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290165,"text":"So how do you convey these 10 things\nin 10 minutes without saying them?"},{"time":293545,"text":"You can't say, \"I've got\nintegrity, invest in me!\""},{"time":295944,"text":"You've got to do a whole pitch\nthat conveys this without conveying it."},{"time":299290,"text":"Think about your pitch as a timeline."},{"time":301081,"text":"It starts off, you walk in the door."},{"time":302987,"text":"They know nothing whatsoever about you."},{"time":304890,"text":"You can take them on an emotional --\nall pitches, all sales presentations,"},{"time":308545,"text":"are emotional at some level."},{"time":309935,"text":"You can go up, you can go down, right?"},{"time":311855,"text":"And it goes from beginning to end."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313503,"text":"You walk in, the first thing\nyou've got to do,"},{"time":315677,"text":"the overall arc of your presentation,\nit's got to start like a rocket."},{"time":319071,"text":"You've got maybe 10 seconds --"},{"time":320830,"text":"between 10 and 30 seconds,\ndepending on how long the pitch is --"},{"time":324014,"text":"to get their attention."},{"time":325562,"text":"In my case, I've invested."},{"time":327032,"text":"I've gotten millions of dollars\nfrom PowerPoint pitches."},{"time":329850,"text":"\"I've invested millions.\"\nThat should get you right there."},{"time":332733,"text":"This can be a fact\nor something counterintuitive."},{"time":335071,"text":"It can be a story or an experience."},{"time":336794,"text":"But you've got to grab\ntheir emotional attention, focused on you,"},{"time":339902,"text":"within that first few seconds."},{"time":341402,"text":"And then from there,\nyou've got to take them"},{"time":343494,"text":"on a very solid, steady, upward path,\nright from beginning to end."},{"time":347382,"text":"Everything has to reinforce this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":348999,"text":"And you've got to get better\nand better and better,"},{"time":351424,"text":"revving up to the very end,"},{"time":352820,"text":"then you've got to -- boom! --"},{"time":354351,"text":"knock them out of the park."},{"time":355677,"text":"You want to get them\nto such an emotional high"},{"time":357860,"text":"they're ready to write you a check,\nthrow money at you,"},{"time":360464,"text":"before you leave."}]},{"cues":[{"time":361639,"text":"How do you do that?"},{"time":362814,"text":"First of all, logical progression."},{"time":364652,"text":"Any time you go backwards,\nany time you skip a step --"},{"time":368035,"text":"imagine walking up a staircase\nwhere some of the treads are missing,"},{"time":371261,"text":"or the heights are different."},{"time":373001,"text":"You stop, you need to figure out\na nice, logical progression."},{"time":375918,"text":"Start with what the market is:\nWhy are you going to do X, Y or Z?"},{"time":379166,"text":"And then you've got to tell me\nhow you're going to do it,"},{"time":381881,"text":"and what you're going to do."},{"time":383430,"text":"And it's got to flow\nfrom beginning to end."}]},{"cues":[{"time":385619,"text":"You've got to let me know\nthere are touchstones,"},{"time":387929,"text":"to tie in to the rest\nof the world out there."},{"time":390103,"text":"For example, reference\ncompanies I've heard of,"},{"time":393425,"text":"or basic items in your business."},{"time":395981,"text":"I want to know about things\nthat I can relate to:"},{"time":398758,"text":"validators, or anything that tells me\nsomebody else has approved this,"},{"time":402479,"text":"or there's outside validation."},{"time":404206,"text":"It can be sales; it can be\nyou got an award for something;"},{"time":407254,"text":"it can be people have done it before;"},{"time":409976,"text":"it can be your beta tests\nare going great, whatever."},{"time":412980,"text":"I want to know validation --\nnot just what you're telling me,"},{"time":415901,"text":"but that somebody\nor something else out there"},{"time":418024,"text":"says this makes sense."},{"time":419282,"text":"And then, I'm looking for the upside;\nI need a believable upside."},{"time":422373,"text":"That's two parts; it's got\nto be upside and believable."},{"time":425023,"text":"The upside means if you tell me\nthat five years out,"},{"time":427527,"text":"you're making a million dollars a year,\nthat's not really upside."},{"time":430610,"text":"Telling me you'll be making\na billion dollars a year --"},{"time":433215,"text":"that's not believable."},{"time":434390,"text":"So it's got to be both."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435565,"text":"On the other hand are things\nthat take the emotional level down."},{"time":438610,"text":"You have to recover from those."},{"time":440113,"text":"For example, anything\nthat I know is not true."},{"time":442284,"text":"\"We have no competition.\nNobody makes a widget like this.\""},{"time":445032,"text":"Odds are I know somebody\nwho's made a widget,"},{"time":447160,"text":"and the minute you tell me that,"},{"time":448792,"text":"I discount half of what\nyou're saying from then on."},{"time":451444,"text":"Anything I don't understand,"},{"time":454213,"text":"where I have to make the leap\nmyself, in my own head,"},{"time":456769,"text":"will stop the flow of the presentation."},{"time":458721,"text":"So you've got to take me\nthrough like a sixth-grader --"},{"time":461326,"text":"dub, dub, dub --\nbut without patronizing me."},{"time":463413,"text":"And it's a very tricky path."},{"time":465000,"text":"But if you can do it,\nit works really well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":467155,"text":"Anything that's inconsistent\nwithin your concept --"},{"time":470861,"text":"if you tell me sales of X, Y or Z\nare 10 million dollars,"},{"time":473561,"text":"five slides later,\nthey're five million dollars ..."},{"time":476019,"text":"One may have been gross sales,\none may have been net sales,"},{"time":478827,"text":"but I want to know that all the numbers\nmake sense together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":481734,"text":"And then, finally: anything\nthat's an error or a typo,"},{"time":484297,"text":"or a stupid mistake or a line\nthat's in the wrong place --"},{"time":487194,"text":"that shows me that if you can't do\na presentation, how can you run a company?"},{"time":490847,"text":"So this all feeds in together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":492743,"text":"The best way to do this\nis to look at our betters,"},{"time":495120,"text":"people who have done this before."},{"time":496739,"text":"Let's look at the most successful\ntechnology executive in the business,"},{"time":500141,"text":"and see how a presentation goes."},{"time":502378,"text":"Bill Gates's PowerPoint\npresentation over here."},{"time":504635,"text":"Here's Gates doing a thing for Windows."},{"time":506707,"text":"Is this how to do a PowerPoint\npresentation? What do you think?"},{"time":509857,"text":"No. Who do you think we should\nlook at as our role model?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":512564,"text":"Oh, isn't that funny!\nThere's another great one over here."},{"time":515388,"text":"OK, Steve Jobs."},{"time":516593,"text":"You want absolute --\nthis is the Zen of presentation, right?"},{"time":520103,"text":"Here he is, one little guy,\nblack jeans and stuff,"},{"time":522913,"text":"on a totally empty stage."},{"time":524129,"text":"What are you focusing on?"},{"time":525731,"text":"You're focusing on him!\nThis is Steve Jobs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":527804,"text":"So are these wonderful long bullet points,\nwhole list of things good?"},{"time":531788,"text":"No, they're not. The long\nbullet points are bad."},{"time":534343,"text":"What's good? Short. Short bullet points."},{"time":536952,"text":"But you know what? Even better than short\nbullet points are no bullet points."},{"time":540632,"text":"Just give me the headline."},{"time":541901,"text":"And you know what?"},{"time":543076,"text":"How many bullet points\ndoes Steve Jobs use?"},{"time":545124,"text":"Basically, none."},{"time":546519,"text":"What do you do?"},{"time":547695,"text":"Best of all, images. Just a simple image."},{"time":550555,"text":"I look at the image;\na picture's worth a thousand words."},{"time":553210,"text":"You look at the image\nand you've got the whole thing."},{"time":555718,"text":"Then you come back to me; you're focused\non me, why I'm such a great guy,"},{"time":559176,"text":"why you want to invest,\nwhy this all makes sense."}]},{"cues":[{"time":561510,"text":"That said, we only have a very short time,"},{"time":563625,"text":"so let's run through the things\nto include in your presentation."},{"time":566687,"text":"First of all, none of these big,\nlong-titled slides"},{"time":569192,"text":"with blah, blah, I'm presenting\nto so-and-so on X date."},{"time":571795,"text":"I know the day, I know who I am --\nI don't need all that."},{"time":574541,"text":"Just give me your company logo."},{"time":576065,"text":"I look at the logo,\nand it ties it to my brain."},{"time":578296,"text":"Then I come back to you.\nI'm focused on you, OK?"},{"time":581716,"text":"You give me your quick, 15-second\nor 30-second intro, grab my attention."},{"time":585665,"text":"Then you give me\na quick business overview."},{"time":587694,"text":"This is not a five-minute pitch.\nThis is, you know, two sentences."},{"time":590845,"text":"\"We build widgets for the X, Y, Z market.\""},{"time":592898,"text":"Or, \"We sell services to help do X.\"\nYou know, whatever."},{"time":595584,"text":"And that is like the picture\non the outside of a jigsaw puzzle box."},{"time":598772,"text":"That lets me know the context."},{"time":600253,"text":"It gives me the armature for the whole\nthing you'll be going through;"},{"time":603529,"text":"it lets me put everything\nin relation to what you've told me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":606415,"text":"Then you've got to walk me through,\nshow me who your management team is."},{"time":610721,"text":"I want to know the size of the market.\nWhy is this market worth getting at?"},{"time":614294,"text":"I want to know your product,\nthat's very important."},{"time":616728,"text":"Now, this is not\na product pitch or sales pitch."},{"time":619003,"text":"I don't want to know all the ins and outs,\njust what the heck is it?"},{"time":622220,"text":"If it's a website, show me\na screenshot of your website."},{"time":625306,"text":"Don't do a live demo.\nNever do a live demo."},{"time":627342,"text":"Do a canned demo,\nor something that lets me know"},{"time":629616,"text":"why people are going\nto buy whatever it is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":631798,"text":"Now that I know what you're selling,"},{"time":634062,"text":"tell me how you make money on it."},{"time":635661,"text":"For every X you sell, you get Y,\nor services of Z."},{"time":640167,"text":"I want to know what the business model\nis on a per-unit basis,"},{"time":643137,"text":"or for the actual product you're selling."},{"time":645121,"text":"I want to know who you're selling to\nin terms of customers"},{"time":647865,"text":"and if you have any special\nrelationships that will help you,"},{"time":650775,"text":"whether it's a distribution relationship\nor a producing partner."},{"time":653809,"text":"Again, validation."},{"time":654984,"text":"This helps to say you're bigger\nthan just one little thing over here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":658259,"text":"But everybody has competition."},{"time":659719,"text":"There's never been a company\nwith no competition,"},{"time":662053,"text":"even if the competition\nis the old way of doing something."},{"time":664806,"text":"I want to know exactly\nwhat your competition is,"},{"time":667110,"text":"and that will help me judge\nhow you fit into the whole operation."},{"time":670201,"text":"I want to know how you're special."}]},{"cues":[{"time":671888,"text":"I know what your competition does --"},{"time":673634,"text":"how are you going to prevent\nthem from eating your lunch?"},{"time":676333,"text":"All this ties into the financial overview."},{"time":678365,"text":"And you can't do a VC pitch\nwithout giving me your financials."},{"time":681317,"text":"I want to know a year or two back,\nor as long as you've been in existence."},{"time":684847,"text":"And I want to know\nfour or five years forward."},{"time":687116,"text":"Five is a bit much. Probably four."}]},{"cues":[{"time":688769,"text":"And I want to know how that business\nmodel, on a product basis,"},{"time":691759,"text":"will translate into a company model:\nHow many widgets will you sell?"},{"time":694987,"text":"You make X amount per widget.\nI want to know what the driver is."},{"time":698014,"text":"We'll have 1,000 customers\nthis year and 10,000 the next,"},{"time":700709,"text":"our revenues will do this and that."},{"time":702404,"text":"That gives me the whole picture\nfor the next several years"},{"time":705149,"text":"into which I'm investing."},{"time":706367,"text":"And I want to know how the money\nfrom me will help you get there."},{"time":709452,"text":"You're going to open\nan offshore plant in China,"},{"time":711717,"text":"you're going to spend it all\non sales and marketing,"},{"time":714180,"text":"you're going to go to Tahiti, whatever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":716067,"text":"But then comes the ask,\nwhere you tell me how much you want."},{"time":718907,"text":"You're looking for 5 million --\nat what valuation?"},{"time":721402,"text":"Two million? 100,000?"},{"time":723636,"text":"What's the money in so far? Who invested?"},{"time":725635,"text":"I hope you invested -- if you can't invest\nin your own thing, why should I?"},{"time":729646,"text":"So I like to know if you have\nfriends and family,"},{"time":731960,"text":"or angel investors, or more VCs before."},{"time":733849,"text":"What's the capital structure\nup until this point?"},{"time":736219,"text":"Finally, having done all that,\nyou've now told me the whole thing,"},{"time":739347,"text":"so now you bring it back\nto that conclusion."},{"time":741862,"text":"This is that rocket going up."},{"time":743282,"text":"Hopefully everything has been positive."},{"time":745176,"text":"And everything you say clicks,\nit all makes sense."},{"time":747647,"text":"And I'm thinking, \"This is really great!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":749648,"text":"Then you take me back\nto just your logo on the screen."},{"time":752219,"text":"And I look at the logo -- OK, good."},{"time":754000,"text":"Now I come back to you.\nNothing else to look at, right?"},{"time":756604,"text":"Now you've got to wrap it up\nto give me the final -- boom! --"},{"time":760151,"text":"the final pitch that's going\nto send me into space."},{"time":762564,"text":"Now, in the process of doing this,"},{"time":764640,"text":"how do you remember\nthe sequences and do it?"},{"time":767119,"text":"You've noticed I'm not looking\nat the screen, right?"},{"time":769580,"text":"The screen is in front of me,"},{"time":771166,"text":"so I couldn't even see if I wanted to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":773001,"text":"So how do I know what's going on?"},{"time":774600,"text":"Well, I have a laptop in front of me."},{"time":776418,"text":"You're looking at me and at this."},{"time":778017,"text":"What am I looking at?"},{"time":779192,"text":"You think that I'm looking at that?"},{"time":780888,"text":"No, I'm looking, actually,"},{"time":782198,"text":"at a special version\nof PowerPoint over here,"},{"time":784562,"text":"which shows me the slides\nahead and behind, my notes,"},{"time":787292,"text":"so I can see what's going on."},{"time":788713,"text":"PowerPoint has this built into\nevery copy of it that's shipped."},{"time":791711,"text":"If you use Apple's Keynote,\nit's got an even better version."},{"time":794554,"text":"There's another program called\nOvation you can get from Adobe"},{"time":797611,"text":"that they bought last summer,"},{"time":799020,"text":"which helps you run the timers\nand lets you figure out what's going on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":802731,"text":"So, here's my wrap-up\nto take you to the moon, right?"},{"time":805313,"text":"I usually do a Top 10,\nbut we don't have time,"},{"time":807491,"text":"so: David's Top Five Presentation Tips."},{"time":809404,"text":"Number five: always use presenter mode,"},{"time":811767,"text":"or Ovation, or presenter tools."},{"time":814164,"text":"It lets you know\nexactly where you're going,"},{"time":816268,"text":"helps you pace yourself,\ngives you a timer, the whole bit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":819168,"text":"Number four: always use remote control."},{"time":821058,"text":"Have you seen me touch\nthe computer? No. Why not?"},{"time":823381,"text":"Because I'm using remote control.\nAlways use remote control."}]},{"cues":[{"time":826222,"text":"Number three: the handouts you give\nare not your presentation."},{"time":829176,"text":"If you follow my suggestions,"},{"time":830588,"text":"you'll have a very spare,\nZen-like presentation,"},{"time":832863,"text":"which is great to convey who you are\nand get people emotionally involved,"},{"time":836319,"text":"but not good as a handout."},{"time":837589,"text":"You want a handout that gives more\ninformation; it has to stand without you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":841190,"text":"Number two: don't read your speech.\nCan you imagine?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":843743,"text":"(Reading) \"You should invest\nin my company ... \""}]},{"cues":[{"time":846012,"text":"It doesn't work."},{"time":847188,"text":"And the number one presentation tip:\nnever, ever look at the screen."},{"time":850813,"text":"You're making a connection\nwith your audience,"},{"time":853021,"text":"and you always want\na one-on-one connection."},{"time":855523,"text":"The screen should come up behind you"},{"time":857582,"text":"and supplement what you're doing,\ninstead of replace you."},{"time":860277,"text":"And that is how to pitch to a VC."}]}]}